eDP1.5 allows Panel Replay on eDP as well. Take this into account when
enabling sink PSR/Panel Replay. Write also PANEL_REPLAY_CONFIG2 register
accordingly.

Signed-off-by: Jouni HÃ¶gander <jouni.hogander@intel.com>
